WEBVTT

00:03.834 --> 00:07.007
DON'T TOUCH THAT DIAL!
IT'S A POP QUIZ.

00:07.007 --> 00:09.630
[ STUDENTS GROAN ]
I KNOW. I KNOW. OKAY, YOU READY?

00:09.630 --> 00:13.474
TURN IT OVER AND START...NOW!

00:19.100 --> 00:21.772
I, UH, THINK
THERE MIGHT BE A MISTAKE.

00:21.772 --> 00:24.355
THE ANSWERS ARE STAPLED
TO THE TEST.

00:24.355 --> 00:25.986
CORRECT!

00:25.986 --> 00:27.608
BEFORE MISS GOODY-TWO-SHOES
HERE BLEW THE WHISTLE,

00:27.608 --> 00:29.820
THE NEURONS IN YOUR VENTROMEDIAL

00:29.820 --> 00:31.822
AND DORSOLATERAL
PREFRONTAL CORTICES

00:31.822 --> 00:33.454
WERE FIRING ON ALL CYLINDERS,

00:33.454 --> 00:35.456
CREATING A RUSH OF ADRENALINE
AND DOPAMINE

00:35.456 --> 00:38.079
NOT UNLIKE A BOXER
ABOUT TO ENTER THE RING.

00:38.079 --> 00:42.293
BUT THE FIGHT HERE WAS BETWEEN
IMPULSE AND SELF-CONTROL.

00:42.293 --> 00:44.375
IT'S CALLED TEMPTATION.

00:44.375 --> 00:46.967
NOW, HER COGNITIVE
CONTROL MECHANISMS

00:46.967 --> 00:48.719
STOPPED HER FROM CHEATING,

00:48.719 --> 00:51.882
BUT SOME OF YOU WERE
ABOUT TO GO THROUGH WITH IT.

00:51.882 --> 00:53.974
I KNOW YOU WERE.
YEAH. RIGHT?
[ LAUGHTER ]

00:53.974 --> 00:55.636
YOUR --
YOUR SELF-CONTROL WAS HYPED

00:55.636 --> 00:57.478
BY THE MORE EMOTIONAL
AND IMPULSIVE LIMBIC SYSTEM,

00:57.478 --> 00:58.889
WHICH WANTED THE EASY "A."

00:58.889 --> 01:00.441
THAT'S BAD.

01:00.441 --> 01:03.444
THAT'S BAD BECAUSE WHEN WE
EXERCISE SELF-RESTRAINT,

01:03.444 --> 01:07.238
WE HAVE GREATER SUCCESS AT WORK,
STRONGER RELATIONSHIPS,

01:07.238 --> 01:08.989
AND BETTER MENTAL HEALTH.

01:08.989 --> 01:12.903
SO, IF IT'S BETTER
TO RESIST TEMPTATION,

01:12.903 --> 01:17.498
WHY DO WE ALWAYS
FIND IT SO EASY TO GIVE IN?

01:17.498 --> 01:20.331
YOU DO REALIZE
I HAVE TO FIT

01:20.331 --> 01:22.163
INTO A WEDDING DRESS
IN A FEW MONTHS.

01:22.163 --> 01:24.585
AH, ONE LOUSY DONUT
WON'T KILL YOU.

01:26.086 --> 01:28.509
[ CHUCKLES ]
HEY.

01:28.509 --> 01:30.591
I WAS THINKING THAT MAYBE
WE COULD STAY IN

01:30.591 --> 01:32.803
FOR A CHANGE ON SATURDAY,
HAVE A MOVIE NIGHT.

01:32.803 --> 01:34.845
I ALREADY HAVE A DATE
ON SATURDAY.

01:34.845 --> 01:37.388
WHAT DO YOU MEAN YOU HAVE A DATE
ON SATURDAY?

01:37.388 --> 01:40.221
WITH MY DAD.
THE BLACKHAWKS GAME.

01:40.221 --> 01:42.483
PLAYOFFS, SECOND ROW,
CENTER ICE.

01:42.483 --> 01:44.064
I FORGOT.
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

01:44.064 --> 01:47.488
MORETTI.

01:47.488 --> 01:48.989
YES, SIR.

01:51.232 --> 01:53.654
I HAVE INTERVIEWED
EVERY WITNESS.

01:53.654 --> 01:55.286
I HAVE COMBED THROUGH
THE FORENSICS.

01:55.286 --> 01:58.659
IF THERE WERE ANY STRONG LEADS,
I PROMISE YOU I --

01:58.659 --> 02:00.501
YES, SIR.

02:01.792 --> 02:04.205
TROUBLE?

02:04.205 --> 02:06.627
I HAVE TO GO TELL
THE PAVEL FAMILY

02:06.627 --> 02:09.510
WHY WE HAVEN'T SOLVED
THEIR DAUGHTER'S MURDER YET.

02:09.510 --> 02:12.513
WE REALLY APPRECIATE YOU
STOPPING BY, AGENT MORETTI.

02:12.513 --> 02:13.924
YEAH.

02:13.924 --> 02:15.756
THESE LAST COUPLE OF WEEKS,
YOU KNOW,

02:15.756 --> 02:20.181
NOT HEARING ANYTHING, IT'S --
IT'S -- IT'S BEEN HELL.

02:20.181 --> 02:21.562
WELL, LET ME ASSURE YOU

02:21.562 --> 02:22.973
THIS IS VERY MUCH
AN ACTIVE INVESTIGATION.

02:22.973 --> 02:24.605
WE ARE PURSUING
EVERY POSSIBLE LEAD --

02:24.605 --> 02:26.357
SO, BASICALLY,
YOU'VE GOT NOTHING.

02:26.357 --> 02:28.859
JUNIOR.
SHOW A LITTLE RESPECT.

02:28.859 --> 02:32.533
I'M SORRY. THE BOYS ARE
A LITTLE ROUGH AROUND THE EDGES.

02:32.533 --> 02:34.365
BUT THEY LOVED
THEIR LITTLE SISTER.

02:34.365 --> 02:36.116
SHE WAS AN ANGEL.

02:36.116 --> 02:38.199
YEAH, AND IT GOT HER KILLED
AND THROWN IN A DITCH.

02:38.199 --> 02:39.370
JUNIOR.

02:42.203 --> 02:43.834
NOW, WHAT ABOUT
THAT VIDEO ONLINE?

02:43.834 --> 02:46.457
YOU'RE NOT LOOKING INTO IT
AS A POSSIBLE LEAD?

02:46.457 --> 02:49.089
I WASN'T AWARE
OF ANY VIDEO.

02:49.089 --> 02:50.711
Max:
YOU WANT SOME POPCORN, DOC?

02:50.711 --> 02:53.554
WHY WOULD
I WANT POPCORN?

02:53.554 --> 02:55.296
IT HAS
NO NUTRITIONAL VALUE,

02:55.296 --> 02:56.717
EXORBITANT LEVELS
OF SODIUM.

02:56.717 --> 02:58.719
YOU MIGHT WANT POPCORN...

02:58.719 --> 03:03.644
BECAUSE I'M ABOUT
TO PUT ON A SHOW.

03:03.644 --> 03:05.185
I'VE BEEN STUDYING UP --

03:05.185 --> 03:07.808
TACTICAL POSITIONS, BACK-RANK
ENDGAMES, MATING NETS.

03:07.808 --> 03:10.901
I EVEN ADDED THE FIANCHETTO
TO MY REPERTOIRE.

03:10.901 --> 03:14.114
NOT INTERESTED.
OH, WHY NOT PLAY?

03:14.114 --> 03:16.527
MAX IS JUST TRYING TO CONNECT.
HAVE SOME FUN.

03:16.527 --> 03:18.529
GIVING A CHESS TUTORIAL
TO A RANK AMATEUR

03:18.529 --> 03:20.371
IS NOT MY IDEA OF FUN.

03:20.371 --> 03:22.993
OH, YOU'RE JUST SCARED.

03:22.993 --> 03:24.415
MM-HMM.
AND YOU SHOULD BE.

03:24.415 --> 03:27.167
I MEAN, YOUR POSITIONAL PLAY
IS SO WEAK,

03:27.167 --> 03:28.789
IT NEEDS TO HIRE
A PERSONAL TRAINER.

03:28.789 --> 03:30.170
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:30.170 --> 03:33.834
ARE YOU CHESS
TRASH-TALKING ME?

03:33.834 --> 03:37.047
WHY?
CAN'T HANDLE THE HEAT?

03:37.047 --> 03:38.839
Natalie: YEAH, DANIEL.

03:38.839 --> 03:41.472
MAYBE YOU'RE WORRIED
THAT HE'LL ACTUALLY BEAT YOU.

03:41.472 --> 03:43.344
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:44.345 --> 03:46.767
FINE. FINE, ONE GAME.

03:46.767 --> 03:48.349
BUT YOU ARE DIGGING YOURSELF
A HOLE, LEWICKI.

03:48.349 --> 03:49.980
OH, YEAH.
A "HOLE" LOT OF AWESOME, DOC.

03:49.980 --> 03:51.982
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

03:51.982 --> 03:56.357
YOUR INEVITABLE HUMILIATION
WILL HAVE TO WAIT.

04:00.200 --> 04:02.202
ANY INTEREST IN HELPING ME
SOLVE THE CASE

04:02.202 --> 04:03.704
THAT WILL NOT BE SOLVED?

04:03.704 --> 04:05.326
ABSOLUTELY.

04:05.326 --> 04:07.628
GOOD, BECAUSE RIGHT NOW
MY ONLY SUSPECT IS THE DEVIL.

04:14.044 --> 04:18.299
THE VICTIM IS SILVIE PAVEL.
SHE'S A STANFORD GRAD.

04:18.299 --> 04:21.302
HER FATHER OWNS A SUCCESSFUL
FLOORING COMPANY IN GLENVIEW.

04:21.302 --> 04:24.515
SILVIE WAS THE IDEALIST
OF THE FAMILY.

04:24.515 --> 04:27.648
SHE WORKED FOR AN INNER-CITY
CHARITY CALLED NRP.

04:27.648 --> 04:28.889
WHAT'S THAT?

04:28.889 --> 04:30.391
NEIGHBORHOOD RELIEF PROJECT.
MM.

04:30.391 --> 04:32.653
THEY DID ANTI-GANG WORK --
JOB TRAINING FOR EX-CONS.

04:32.653 --> 04:35.065
THEY HANDED OUT
MICROLOANS.

04:35.065 --> 04:36.897
SILVIE WAS DOING OUTREACH
FOR THEM IN ALBANY PARK

04:36.897 --> 04:39.029
WHEN SHE WENT MISSING
LAST MONTH.
A ROUGH PART OF TOWN.

04:39.029 --> 04:40.321
YEAH.
DEALERS RUN THOSE STREETS.

04:40.321 --> 04:42.162
SO YOU THINK
IT'S DRUG-RELATED?

04:42.162 --> 04:44.995
DON'T KNOW. [ SIGHS ]

04:44.995 --> 04:46.747
BUT A WEEK AFTER SILVIE
WENT MISSING,

04:46.747 --> 04:48.959
HER BODY TURNED UP
ACROSS STATE LINES

04:48.959 --> 04:50.751
UNDER A BRIDGE IN
MARQUETTE PARK, INDIANA.

04:50.751 --> 04:53.253
THAT'S WHY THE FBI
GOT CALLED IN.

04:53.253 --> 04:55.416
HORRIBLE.
CAUSE OF DEATH?

04:55.416 --> 04:59.049
MASSIVE TRAUMA TO THE HEAD,
CHEST, AND ABDOMEN.

04:59.049 --> 05:01.682
NO FINGERPRINTS, NO DNA,
NO MURDER WEAPON.

05:01.682 --> 05:03.884
WE DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHERE SHE DIED.

05:03.884 --> 05:06.016
OKAY, SO, WHERE DOES
THE DEVIL COME IN?

05:08.188 --> 05:10.811
I'M ASH-SHAYTAN!

05:10.811 --> 05:13.694
THE ARCHFIEND!

05:13.694 --> 05:15.436
THE BEAST WITH NO BODY!

05:15.436 --> 05:18.649
I KILLED SILVIE!

05:18.649 --> 05:21.862
PUT HER BODY IN THE GROUND,
AND HER SOUL IS MINE NOW!

05:21.862 --> 05:24.705
SILVIE'S BOSS,
ELENA DOUGLAS.

05:24.705 --> 05:26.537
SHE AND HER HUSBAND, RICHARD,
RUN THE CHARITY.

05:26.537 --> 05:29.329
WE VETTED HER AT THE OUTSET
OF THE INVESTIGATION,

05:29.329 --> 05:31.251
BUT SHE AND SILVIE
HAD A GREAT RELATIONSHIP.

05:31.251 --> 05:33.163
THERE WAS NO REASON
TO SERIOUSLY SUSPECT HER.

05:33.163 --> 05:34.375
UH-HUH.

05:34.375 --> 05:36.216
EXCEPT FOR
THE ACUTE PSYCHOSIS.

05:36.216 --> 05:38.419
ELENA HAD NO HISTORY
OF MENTAL ILLNESS.

05:38.419 --> 05:40.421
BUT THEN, A FEW DAYS
AFTER SILVIE DIED,

05:40.421 --> 05:42.883
SHE WAS HOSPITALIZED
WITH PSYCHOTIC SYMPTOMS,

05:42.883 --> 05:44.385
DIAGNOSED
WITH SCHIZOPHRENIA.

05:44.385 --> 05:46.387
UH-HUH.
NOW SHE'S A SUSPECT.

05:46.387 --> 05:48.599
SHE IS THE ONLY LEAD
THAT WE HAVE HAD IN WEEKS.

05:48.599 --> 05:50.431
COULD YOU JUST TALK TO HER?
TELL ME WHAT YOU THINK?

05:50.431 --> 05:53.474
OKAY.
OKAY, WHAT HOSPITAL?

05:53.474 --> 05:55.736
ACTUALLY, UH, HER HUSBAND
HAD HER DISCHARGED.

05:55.736 --> 05:59.319
HE WAS UPSET THAT
SHE WASN'T GETTING BETTER.

05:59.319 --> 06:01.071
SHE'S AT HOME.
[ SIGHS ]

06:01.071 --> 06:04.485
YOU CAN'T COME IN.
I'M SORRY, BUT ELENA'S RESTING.

06:04.485 --> 06:07.077
Elena: STOP!
MAKE IT STOP, PLEASE!

06:10.411 --> 06:12.493
NO, STOP, PLEASE! STOP!

06:12.493 --> 06:14.415
STOP! MAKE IT STOP!
PLEASE!

06:14.415 --> 06:16.997
DEPART INTO
THE EVERLASTING FIRE.

06:16.997 --> 06:19.169
[ SCREAMS ]
VIRTUS CHRISTI COGERIS.
GOD HIMSELF COMMANDS YOU.

06:19.169 --> 06:22.172
AAH! PLEASE MAKE IT STOP!
IT BURNS!

06:22.172 --> 06:23.764
WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON HERE?!

06:23.764 --> 06:26.006
THE RITE OF EXORCISM.
PLEASE, I NEED YOU TO LEAVE.

06:26.006 --> 06:27.508
WE'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE

06:27.508 --> 06:29.770
UNTIL YOU STOP THIS ARCHAIC
TORTURE RITUAL.

06:29.770 --> 06:31.181
THIS WOMAN SHOULD BE
IN A HOSPITAL.

06:31.181 --> 06:33.103
WE GAVE MODERN MEDICINE
A CHANCE.

06:33.103 --> 06:35.726
T-THE DOCTORS GAVE HER
A MILLION ANTI-PSYCHOTICS,

06:35.726 --> 06:37.568
AND NONE WORKED.

06:37.568 --> 06:40.190
THIS IS PART OF ELENA'S FAITH.
IT'S WHAT SHE WOULD WANT.

06:40.190 --> 06:42.693
SHE'S SCREAMING FOR HELP.
SHE'S SCREAMING
FOR DELIVERANCE.

06:42.693 --> 06:43.944
HER WRISTS ARE BLEEDING!

06:43.944 --> 06:45.786
PEOPLE HAVE DIED
DURING EXORCISMS.

06:45.786 --> 06:47.618
LISTEN, UNLESS YOU GET HER OUT
OF THOSE RESTRAINTS RIGHT NOW,

06:47.618 --> 06:49.870
I AM BRINGING YOU BOTH IN
FOR ENDANGERMENT.

06:49.870 --> 06:53.373
THIS IS A CHURCH-SANCTIONED
EXORCISM, YOUNG LADY.

06:53.373 --> 06:56.206
ACTUALLY, IT'S SPECIAL AGENT
KATE MORETTI.

06:56.206 --> 06:58.128
I HAPPEN TO BE
A GOOD CATHOLIC,

06:58.128 --> 07:00.340
SO THE LAST THING I WANT TO DO
IS ARREST A PRIEST,

07:00.340 --> 07:01.802
BUT I WILL IF I HAVE TO.

07:03.133 --> 07:06.807
[ GROANING ]

07:06.807 --> 07:08.889
YOU'RE GIVING SATAN
EXACTLY WHAT HE WANTS.

07:08.889 --> 07:10.551
THERE IS NO SATAN.

07:10.551 --> 07:11.892
THIS WOMAN IS SUFFERING
FROM PSYCHIATRIC SYMPTOMS --

07:11.892 --> 07:13.393
HALLUCINATIONS, DELUSIONS.

07:13.393 --> 07:15.556
PEOPLE LIKE YOU ARE
UNCOMFORTABLE WITH IT,

07:15.556 --> 07:17.728
SO YOU CALL HER POSSESSED
AND -- AND PERSECUTE HER.

07:17.728 --> 07:18.979
IT'S BEEN GOING ON
FOR MILLENNIA.

07:18.979 --> 07:19.980
DANIEL.

07:19.980 --> 07:24.234
ELENA. I'M DR. PIERCE.

07:24.234 --> 07:26.066
CAN YOU HEAR ME?
YOU GET AWAY!

07:26.066 --> 07:27.988
YOU GET AWAY FROM ME!
MY SOUL BELONGS TO SATAN!

07:27.988 --> 07:29.159
I TRIED TO TELL YOU.
[ SCREAMS ]

07:29.159 --> 07:30.330
WILL YOU GET THEM
OUT OF HERE?

07:30.330 --> 07:31.331
FATHER, PLEASE.

07:34.915 --> 07:36.336
[ GRUNTING ]

07:42.583 --> 07:44.795
HERE. I WANT TO TRY TO
HELP YOU IF I CAN.

07:44.795 --> 07:47.427
Satan:
AH, BUT YOU CAN'T.

07:47.427 --> 07:53.433
UNLESS, OF COURSE, I AGREE
TO RELINQUISH HER SOUL.

07:53.433 --> 07:55.185
[ SIGHS ]
PLEASE, YOU DON'T EXIST.

07:55.185 --> 07:57.808
WHAT?
[ LAUGHS ]

07:57.808 --> 08:00.020
YOU THINK
YOU'RE HALLUCINATING.

08:00.020 --> 08:01.772
OF COURSE I AM.
OH.

08:01.772 --> 08:03.153
I MEAN
YOU DON'T EXIST AT ALL.

08:03.153 --> 08:05.155
YOU'RE A MYTHICAL
PERSONIFICATION OF EVIL

08:05.155 --> 08:07.447
USED TO EXPLAIN AWAY SUFFERING
IN THE WORLD.

08:07.447 --> 08:09.700
I SEE.
MAKE IT STOP!

08:09.700 --> 08:11.702
I'VE GOT MY HAND WRAPPED AROUND
THIS WOMAN'S SOUL.

08:11.702 --> 08:13.534
I CAN TEAR IT
FROM HER BODY.

08:15.455 --> 08:18.458
BUT IF YOU PROMISE ME YOUR SOUL
IN EXCHANGE FOR HERS,

08:18.458 --> 08:19.790
I CAN, UH...

08:23.624 --> 08:25.546
...GIVE YOU THE CURE
FOR WHAT AILS HER.

08:25.546 --> 08:29.550
I THINK I KNOW WHAT'S WRONG
WITH YOU.

08:29.550 --> 08:32.633
IT COULD BE A TERATOMA,
WHICH IS A KIND OF TUMOR.

08:32.633 --> 08:35.055
FIRST, THEY SAY SCHIZOPHRENIA,
NOW A TUMOR.

08:35.055 --> 08:36.687
RICHARD,
LET ME FINISH MY WORK.

08:36.687 --> 08:38.478
TERATOMAS ARE RARE,
BUT IF IT'S OVARIAN,

08:38.478 --> 08:40.480
IT CAN CAUSE A KIND
OF ENCEPHALITIS,

08:40.480 --> 08:42.482
WHICH IS OFTEN MISDIAGNOSED
AS SCHIZOPHRENIA.

08:42.482 --> 08:44.645
THAT WOULD EXPLAIN WHY
THE ANTI-PSYCHOTICS DIDN'T HELP.

08:44.645 --> 08:46.907
REMOVE THE TUMOR
FROM HER OVARY,

08:46.907 --> 08:48.739
AND HER BRAIN FUNCTION
MAY RETURN TO NORMAL.

08:48.739 --> 08:51.491
BUT YOU -- YOU HAVE TO LET ME
TAKE HER BACK TO THE HOSPITAL.

08:51.491 --> 08:54.494
OKAY. FINE.

08:54.494 --> 08:55.916
I'LL CALL AN AMBULANCE.

08:59.499 --> 09:03.924
LOOKS LIKE WE GOT A DEAL,
EH, DANNY BOY?

09:03.924 --> 09:06.006
I'LL GET STARTED
ON THE PAPERWORK.

09:06.006 --> 09:11.091
REAL PLEASURE
DOING BUSINESS WITH YOU.

09:16.056 --> 09:18.388
TERATOMA COMES FROM
THE GREEK WORD "TERATON,"

09:18.388 --> 09:19.389
WHICH MEANS "MONSTER."

09:19.389 --> 09:20.811
THIS PARTICULAR MONSTER

09:20.811 --> 09:22.482
WAS WRAPPED AROUND
ELENA'S LEFT OVARY.

09:22.482 --> 09:23.984
OH, MY GOD.
YEAH.

09:23.984 --> 09:26.146
TERATOMAS ARE MADE UP OF CELLS
FROM OTHER ORGANS.

09:26.146 --> 09:28.568
YOU CAN SEE THE HAIR,
THE TEETH.

09:28.568 --> 09:30.991
SOME GROW PARTIAL HANDS,
EYES,

09:30.991 --> 09:32.903
EVEN A RUDIMENTARY,
BEATING HEART.

09:32.903 --> 09:36.156
BUT THE REAL CULPRIT HERE
IS INVISIBLE.

09:36.156 --> 09:38.158
ELENA'S TERATOMA
CAUSED ANTIBODIES

09:38.158 --> 09:40.330
TO TARGET NMDA RECEPTORS
IN HER BRAIN.

09:40.330 --> 09:41.962
THAT LED TO HER
PSYCHOTIC BEHAVIOR,

09:41.962 --> 09:43.253
HER MEMORY DISTURBANCES,

09:43.253 --> 09:45.465
AND THE BELIEF
THAT SHE KILLED SILVIE.

09:45.465 --> 09:47.377
FOR HER,
THE SYMPTOMS MANIFESTED

09:47.377 --> 09:49.259
AS RELIGIOUSLY BASED
DELUSIONS.

09:49.259 --> 09:51.762
DIVINE PROVIDENCE
BROUGHT YOU TO ELENA.

09:51.762 --> 09:53.513
THANK GOD
YOU CAME ALONG.

09:53.513 --> 09:56.216
SO YOU ADMIT THIS HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH THE DEVIL?

09:56.216 --> 09:58.268
I'M NOT A PHILISTINE,
DR. PIERCE.

09:58.268 --> 10:01.021
I PRAY THIS SURGERY HAS CURED
ELENA'S SUFFERING.

10:01.021 --> 10:02.482
BUT JUST BECAUSE
YOU FOUND A TUMOR

10:02.482 --> 10:05.525
DOESN'T MEAN THE DEVIL
DIDN'T PUT IT THERE.

10:05.525 --> 10:08.278
Richard:
ALL I CARE ABOUT IS WHETHER
SHE'S GONNA BE NORMAL AGAIN.

10:08.278 --> 10:10.440
WILL I GET MY WIFE BACK?

10:10.440 --> 10:12.192
WE SHOULD KNOW
BY THE MORNING.

10:16.657 --> 10:18.288
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

10:21.702 --> 10:25.335
FATHER PAT.
DO COME IN.

10:26.626 --> 10:29.840
SORRY TO BOTHER YOU
THIS LATE, KATIE.

10:32.462 --> 10:35.135
HAVEN'T SEEN YOU AT CONFESSION
FOR A WHILE.

10:35.135 --> 10:36.967
THAT WOULD PROBABLY BE BECAUSE
I HAVE NOTHING TO CONFESS.

10:36.967 --> 10:38.809
OH, REALLY?

10:38.809 --> 10:40.430
SO, IT'S NOT TRUE THAT
YOU GOT A LITTLE SURLY

10:40.430 --> 10:41.972
WITH A CERTAIN MONSIGNOR
THIS MORNING?

10:41.972 --> 10:46.316
BOY, YOU GUYS TRADE GOSSIP
FASTER THAN PEREZ HILTON.

10:46.316 --> 10:48.068
AND, NO, FOR THE RECORD,

10:48.068 --> 10:50.070
I DID NOT GET A LITTLE SURLY
WITH ANYONE THIS MORNING.

10:50.070 --> 10:51.571
I WAS JUST DOING MY JOB.

10:51.571 --> 10:53.403
WELL, MAYBE, BUT REMEMBER
HOW I TOLD DONNIE

10:53.403 --> 10:55.235
THAT I WOULD PULL
A FEW STRINGS

10:55.235 --> 10:56.656
TO GET YOUR ORIGINAL
MARRIAGE ANNULLED

10:56.656 --> 10:58.238
SO THE DIVORCE
WOULDN'T COUNT

10:58.238 --> 10:59.409
AND YOU COULD GET HITCHED
AT ST. MARY'S, RIGHT?

10:59.409 --> 11:01.081
YEAH.

11:01.081 --> 11:03.493
LUCK OF THE IRISH --
MONSIGNOR NORRIS IS THE GUY

11:03.493 --> 11:05.335
I WAS GONNA PULL
THOSE STRINGS WITH.

11:05.335 --> 11:08.088
YIKES.
YEAH, SO,
SUFFICE IT TO SAY,

11:08.088 --> 11:09.920
YOU AND DONNIE ARE OFF
THE CHURCH CALENDAR,

11:09.920 --> 11:12.002
AND YOUR ANNULMENT IS, UH,

11:12.002 --> 11:14.094
ON A SLOW TRAIN
TO SIBERIA.

11:14.094 --> 11:15.716
[ SIGHS ]

11:15.716 --> 11:19.559
LOOK, DONNIE REALLY HAS
HIS HEART SET ON THIS.

11:19.559 --> 11:21.932
WHAT DO I DO TO FIX IT?

11:21.932 --> 11:23.563
KATE, I'VE KNOWN YOU
SINCE KINDERGARTEN.

11:23.563 --> 11:25.185
I'M PRETTY SURE
YOU'RE NOT GONNA LIKE IT.

11:25.185 --> 11:28.188
LOOK, AS LONG AS HE DOESN'T
EXPECT ME TO SLINK OVER THERE

11:28.188 --> 11:29.609
WITH MY TAIL
BETWEEN MY LEGS,

11:29.609 --> 11:31.772
MAKE SOME SORT OF BIG,
FORMAL APOLOGY...

11:31.772 --> 11:34.194
HE WANTS A FORMAL APOLOGY.
SON OF A --

11:35.365 --> 11:37.367
...BISCUIT. BISCUIT.

11:38.949 --> 11:41.161
Richard:
IT WAS A MIRACLE.

11:41.161 --> 11:43.623
ELENA WOKE UP LUCID.
SHE'S STILL WEAK, BUT...

11:43.623 --> 11:46.456
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
[ SIGHS ]

11:46.456 --> 11:48.288
SHE'S THE SAME WOMAN SHE WAS
BEFORE SHE GOT SICK.

11:48.288 --> 11:50.791
ARE YOU THE DOCTOR
THAT DIAGNOSED MY TUMOR?

11:50.791 --> 11:53.884
YES. DO YOU REMEMBER
MEETING ME YESTERDAY?

11:55.135 --> 11:58.138
I'M AGENT KATE MORETTI.
DO YOU REMEMBER ME?

11:58.138 --> 12:01.551
WE SPOKE AFTER SILVIE
DISAPPEARED.

12:01.551 --> 12:05.185
I WANTED TO TALK TO YOU AGAIN
BECAUSE YOU...

12:05.185 --> 12:07.647
SAID SOME PRETTY CRAZY THINGS
WHEN YOU WERE SICK.

12:07.647 --> 12:10.650
RICHARD TOLD ME.

12:10.650 --> 12:13.483
THAT'S WHY MY LAWYER
IS HERE.

12:13.483 --> 12:15.735
BRENDAN VOSS.

12:17.197 --> 12:20.410
YOU SAID THAT YOU WERE
POSSESSED BY SATAN

12:20.410 --> 12:23.914
AND THAT YOU KILLED SILVIE
AND BURIED HER BODY.

12:23.914 --> 12:25.665
I WAS NOT POSSESSED
BY SATAN.

12:25.665 --> 12:27.077
OF COURSE NOT.

12:27.077 --> 12:29.079
BUT I DID KILL SILVIE.

12:30.420 --> 12:33.253
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED.

12:33.253 --> 12:36.877
I HAD BEEN HEARING VOICES.

12:36.877 --> 12:40.510
THEY TOLD ME THAT SILVIE
WAS...EVIL,

12:40.510 --> 12:42.843
THE CAUSE OF ALL
OF MY SUFFERING.

12:44.514 --> 12:46.346
THAT NIGHT, THEY TOLD ME...

12:46.346 --> 12:48.939
TO GET IN MY CAR
AND GO FIND HER.

12:50.440 --> 12:51.731
[ Voice breaking ]
I FINALLY SAW HER

12:51.731 --> 12:54.734
IN FRONT OF
A CLIENT'S APARTMENT.

12:54.734 --> 12:58.949
AND THE VOICES TOLD ME
THAT SHE WAS A MONSTER...

12:58.949 --> 13:01.161
AND THAT I HAD TO DESTROY HER,

13:01.161 --> 13:03.703
SO I HIT THE GAS PEDAL
AND I RAN HER DOWN.

13:05.956 --> 13:08.038
BUT THEY DIDN'T STOP.
THEY TOLD ME...

13:08.038 --> 13:09.870
TO HIDE THE BODY,
SO I PUT HER IN THE CAR,

13:09.870 --> 13:12.082
AND -- AND I DROVE

13:12.082 --> 13:15.375
TO MARQUETTE PARK
AND LEFT HER THERE.

13:17.467 --> 13:19.049
I'M SO SORRY.

13:19.049 --> 13:20.881
WE'RE OBVIOUSLY PLEADING

13:20.881 --> 13:23.803
NOT GUILTY
BY REASON OF INSANITY,

13:23.803 --> 13:25.385
AND, DR. PIERCE, I ASSUME

13:25.385 --> 13:26.977
YOU'LL BE TESTIFYING
ON ELENA'S BEHALF.

13:29.139 --> 13:31.561
I DID NOT SEE THAT COMING.
DID YOU?

13:31.561 --> 13:34.314
WHEN YOU INTERVIEWED HER
THE FIRST TIME,

13:34.314 --> 13:35.896
DID SHE SEEM STABLE?
YEAH.

13:35.896 --> 13:38.028
BUT, LIKE I SAID,
IT WAS A SHORT MEETING,

13:38.028 --> 13:40.650
AND WE DIDN'T REALLY THINK
OF HER AS A SUSPECT.
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATION ]

13:40.650 --> 13:42.072
SEE YOU SOON?

13:42.072 --> 13:43.153
GOT TO GO.
EXCUSE ME A MINUTE.

13:44.744 --> 13:46.746
MONSIGNOR.

13:46.746 --> 13:49.119
I'M, UH, HAPPY TO SEE
YOU HERE, ACTUALLY.

13:49.119 --> 13:51.001
I WANTED TO SAY
THAT I AM SORRY

13:51.001 --> 13:53.503
IF THERE WAS ANY
MISUNDERSTANDING YESTERDAY.

13:53.503 --> 13:57.507
I MEANT YOU NO OFFENSE.
I WAS JUST DOING MY JOB.

13:57.507 --> 13:59.339
HMM.

13:59.339 --> 14:03.343
AN APOLOGY WITH AN EXCUSE
IS NOT TRUE REPENTANCE.

14:03.343 --> 14:05.926
MONSIGNOR,
I'M -- I'M TRYING HERE.

14:05.926 --> 14:08.929
MY CHILD, I'VE TAKEN CONFESSION
FOR 25 YEARS.

14:08.929 --> 14:12.022
I CAN RECOGNIZE FALSE CONTRITION
WHEN I HEAR IT.

14:12.022 --> 14:16.436
OKAY, YOU KNOW WHAT? FINE.
I AM GOOD AT MY JOB.

14:16.436 --> 14:19.529
AND FRANKLY, I ONLY DID WHAT
ANY DECENT AGENT WOULD DO.

14:19.529 --> 14:22.362
WELL, YOU'VE CERTAINLY MADE
YOUR TRUE FEELINGS CLEAR.

14:26.616 --> 14:28.038
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

14:28.038 --> 14:31.451
HEY, DANNY BOY.

14:31.451 --> 14:33.083
OH, WHY ARE YOU
STILL HERE?

14:33.083 --> 14:34.334
I'M JUST FINALIZING
OUR AGREEMENT.

14:34.334 --> 14:37.207
I HAD MY TEAM OF LAWYERS
DRAW IT UP.

14:37.207 --> 14:38.628
A LOT OF THOSE GUYS
DOWN THERE --

14:38.628 --> 14:40.630
THROW A ROCK, HIT A LAWYER.
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:40.630 --> 14:43.303
ACTUALLY, IT'S A PRETTY POPULAR
PASTIME FOR US.

14:43.303 --> 14:45.505
SO, YOU CAN HAVE
WHATEVER YOU WANT --

14:45.505 --> 14:48.508
FAME, FORTUNE,
CUBS WORLD CHAMPIONSHIP.

14:48.508 --> 14:50.220
[ LAUGHS ]

14:50.220 --> 14:54.434
BUT, UH, MAKE SURE YOU READ
THE FINE PRINT BEFORE YOU SIGN.

14:54.434 --> 14:56.316
YOU KNOW WHAT THEY SAY.

14:56.316 --> 14:59.069
THE DEVIL
IS IN THE DETAILS.

14:59.069 --> 15:02.902
THE DETAILS.

15:04.734 --> 15:07.988
Y-YOU KNOW THAT STORY
THAT ELENA JUST TOLD US?

15:09.489 --> 15:11.992
IT'S ALL A LIE.

15:19.089 --> 15:20.710
THE ANTIBODIES CREATED TO FIGHT
THIS KIND OF TUMOR

15:20.710 --> 15:22.042
WREAK HAVOC WITH --
WITH A LOT OF BRAIN FUNCTIONS,

15:22.042 --> 15:23.843
PARTICULARLY MEMORY.

15:23.843 --> 15:27.427
TERATOMA PATIENTS ALMOST ALWAYS
HAVE SOME FORM OF AMNESIA.

15:27.427 --> 15:29.259
SO, IF ELENA
REALLY HAD BEEN PSYCHOTIC

15:29.259 --> 15:31.681
AT THE TIME OF THE KILLING,
SHE WOULDN'T BE ABLE TO REMEMBER

15:31.681 --> 15:33.763
ALL OF THE DETAILS
SHE DESCRIBED.

15:33.763 --> 15:35.355
MAYBE THE LAWYER
COACHED HER.

15:35.355 --> 15:37.687
WHY COACH A CLIENT TO BE --
TO BE STRONG ON DETAILS

15:37.687 --> 15:39.769
WHEN SHE WAS SUPPOSEDLY
PSYCHOTIC AT THE TIME?

15:39.769 --> 15:41.691
IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.
TIME-OUT.

15:41.691 --> 15:43.523
DANIEL PIERCE
IS STANDING HERE

15:43.523 --> 15:45.525
TELLING ME NOT TO BELIEVE
THE CRAZY PERSON?

15:45.525 --> 15:47.157
I DON'T THINK
ELENA WAS PSYCHOTIC

15:47.157 --> 15:48.948
WHEN SHE KILLED SILVIE.

15:48.948 --> 15:50.870
I THINK SHE'S USING THE TUMOR
SHE GOT LATER AS A COVER-UP.

15:50.870 --> 15:53.873
SO YOU'RE SAYING
THAT SHE WAS SANE ONE DAY

15:53.873 --> 15:56.456
AND THEN INSTITUTIONALIZED
A WEEK LATER

15:56.456 --> 15:57.877
WITH FULL-BLOWN PSYCHOSIS.

15:57.877 --> 15:59.379
TOTALLY PLAUSIBLE
WITH A TERATOMA.

15:59.379 --> 16:01.211
SHE COULD HAVE HAD IT
HER WHOLE LIFE

16:01.211 --> 16:03.213
AND FELT NORMAL, BUT AS SOON AS
THE ENCEPHALITIS DEVELOPED,

16:03.213 --> 16:05.135
HER PSYCHOTIC SYMPTOMS
WERE TRIGGERED.

16:05.135 --> 16:09.219
SO YOU THINK ELENA
KILLED SILVIE IN COLD BLOOD?

16:09.219 --> 16:10.680
OR IT COULD HAVE BEEN
VEHICULAR MANSLAUGHTER.

16:10.680 --> 16:12.302
SHE COULD HAVE RUN SILVIE DOWN
IN THE ROAD

16:12.302 --> 16:15.145
WHEN SHE WAS HIGH
OR TEXTING OR DRINKING

16:15.145 --> 16:16.806
AND THEN PANICKED
AND HID THE BODY.

16:16.806 --> 16:18.858
ONE WAY OR ANOTHER,
IT'S A BRILLIANT PLAN.

16:18.858 --> 16:20.860
H-HER CONFESSION STOPS
THE INVESTIGATION.

16:20.860 --> 16:23.363
SHE PLEADS NOT GUILTY
BY REASON OF INSANITY,

16:23.363 --> 16:26.406
WHICH NORMALLY MEANS SPENDING
YEARS IN A PSYCH HOSPITAL.

16:26.406 --> 16:28.028
ELENA'S EXAMINED,

16:28.028 --> 16:29.489
FOUND COMPLETELY SANE
NOW THAT HER TUMOR IS GONE.

16:29.489 --> 16:32.072
[ SIGHS ]
SHE'LL WALK.

16:32.072 --> 16:34.824
YOU GOT TO STOP
THAT PLEA.

16:34.824 --> 16:38.498
[ SIGHS ] OKAY.

16:38.498 --> 16:40.290
BUT, DANIEL, YOU'RE THE ONE
THAT DIAGNOSED HER

16:40.290 --> 16:42.122
AND TOLD EVERYONE HOW CRAZY
THAT TUMOR MADE HER.

16:42.122 --> 16:44.334
SO IF I'M GOING TO TRIAL,

16:44.334 --> 16:46.386
I NEED EVIDENCE THAT PROVES
THAT ELENA WASN'T SICK

16:46.386 --> 16:47.677
THE DAY
SILVIE WAS MURDERED.

16:49.589 --> 16:51.681
Jake: I TOLD YOU
EVERYTHING I KNEW A MONTH AGO.

16:51.681 --> 16:54.894
RIGHT, NOW, YOU TOLD US THAT,
WHEN YOU GOT OUT OF PRISON,

16:54.894 --> 16:56.726
ELENA HIRED YOU
TO DRIVE HER AROUND,

16:56.726 --> 16:58.558
ANSWER THE PHONES.

16:58.558 --> 17:00.770
WHAT CAN YOU TELL US
ABOUT HOW SHE WAS ACTING

17:00.770 --> 17:01.981
ON THE NIGHT
THAT SILVIE DISAPPEARED?

17:01.981 --> 17:03.693
WHAT WAS
HER STATE OF MIND?

17:03.693 --> 17:06.106
YEAH, I HEARD
SHE WAS PLEADING INSANITY.

17:06.106 --> 17:08.027
YOU WANT TO KNOW
IF SHE WAS CRAZY?

17:08.027 --> 17:10.240
JUST TELL US
WHAT YOU REMEMBER.

17:10.240 --> 17:12.702
I DROVE ELENA
TO THE HYATT.

17:12.702 --> 17:15.655
SHE GAVE A PRESENTATION TO
SOME BIG, CORPORATE FAT CATS,

17:15.655 --> 17:17.707
TRYING TO GET THEM
TO DONATE TO NRP.

17:17.707 --> 17:19.869
AND SHE WAS FINE,
NO ERRATIC BEHAVIOR?

17:22.372 --> 17:25.795
DID SOMETHING HAPPEN?
AFTER THE PRESENTATION,

17:25.795 --> 17:28.548
WE STOPPED AT THE HOTEL BAR,
HAD A FEW DRINKS.

17:28.548 --> 17:30.880
ELENA STARTED
HITTING ON ME.

17:33.383 --> 17:34.634
SO, WHAT DID YOU DO?

17:34.634 --> 17:37.387
I GOT US A ROOM.

17:39.479 --> 17:41.641
[ BOTH MOANING ]

17:43.233 --> 17:44.814
ELENA, SLOW DOWN.

17:44.814 --> 17:47.567
I DON'T WANT TO SLOW DOWN.
LET'S JUST GET THIS OVER WITH.

17:47.567 --> 17:49.899
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA,
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.

17:51.151 --> 17:52.742
GET IT OVER WITH?

17:52.742 --> 17:55.365
I'M SO SORRY.

17:55.365 --> 17:57.197
THIS IS NOT FAIR
TO YOU.

17:57.197 --> 17:59.409
I'M...

17:59.409 --> 18:02.252
I'M JUST TRYING
TO GET BACK AT RICHARD.

18:02.252 --> 18:03.913
FOR WHAT?

18:03.913 --> 18:05.585
HE'S HAVING AN AFFAIR
WITH SILVIE.

18:05.585 --> 18:07.086
WHAT MAKES YOU
THINK THAT?

18:07.086 --> 18:09.169
'CAUSE I HEARD THEM HAVING
AN ARGUMENT IN HIS OFFICE.

18:09.169 --> 18:11.341
WHAT EXACTLY
DID YOU HEAR?

18:11.341 --> 18:15.175
SILVIE SAID THAT, UM,
SHE COULDN'T KEEP IT A SECRET,

18:15.175 --> 18:18.178
THAT SHE HAD TO TELL ME,
AND RICHARD SAID NO...

18:18.178 --> 18:21.431
THAT IF I FOUND OUT,
IT WOULD DESTROY OUR MARRIAGE.

18:23.022 --> 18:25.435
IT ALL MAKES SENSE NOW.

18:25.435 --> 18:27.647
I MEAN, SHE MUST HAVE BEEN
CRACKING UP, RIGHT?

18:27.647 --> 18:30.440
THAT'S WHY SHE WAS ALL PARANOID
ABOUT RICHARD AND SILVIE.

18:30.440 --> 18:33.693
SO YOU DON'T THINK THAT THEY
WERE HAVING AN AFFAIR?

18:33.693 --> 18:36.115
HELL NO. AND I TOLD ELENA THAT,
BUT SHE WOULDN'T BELIEVE ME.

18:36.115 --> 18:37.947
SHE TOOK OFF UPSET.

18:37.947 --> 18:39.579
ABOUT WHAT TIME
WAS THAT?

18:39.579 --> 18:41.040
I DON'T KNOW.
AROUND 9:00.

18:41.040 --> 18:44.454
THE NEXT DAY, SHE BEGGED ME
NOT TO SAY ANYTHING...

18:44.454 --> 18:46.546
SO I NEVER DID.

18:46.546 --> 18:50.170
SO, ELENA WAS SEXUALLY
AGGRESSIVE AND PARANOID.

18:50.170 --> 18:51.711
COULD THE TUMOR
HAVE CAUSED THAT?

18:51.711 --> 18:53.553
SOUNDS LIKE SHE WAS MORE UPSET
THAN ACUTELY DELUSIONAL.

18:53.553 --> 18:55.014
AND IF
SHE REALLY BELIEVED

18:55.014 --> 18:56.426
THAT SILVIE WAS
HAVING AN AFFAIR WITH RICHARD,

18:56.426 --> 18:58.057
WELL, THAT'S MOTIVE
TO KILL HER, RIGHT?

18:58.057 --> 18:59.429
AND SHE HAD OPPORTUNITY.

18:59.429 --> 19:00.640
FORENSICS ESTIMATES
HER TIME OF DEATH

19:00.640 --> 19:02.061
BETWEEN 10:00
AND MIDNIGHT.

19:02.061 --> 19:04.063
SO, IF SHE LEFT THE HOTEL
AT 9:00,

19:04.063 --> 19:07.317
THAT'S ENOUGH TIME TO GO DOWN
TO ALBANY PARK TO RUN HER DOWN.

19:07.317 --> 19:08.728
SO MAYBE IT WASN'T
VEHICULAR MANSLAUGHTER AT ALL.

19:08.728 --> 19:10.149
MAYBE
IT WAS PREMEDITATED MURDER

19:10.149 --> 19:12.482
BY SOMEONE THAT KNEW EXACTLY
WHAT SHE WAS DOING.

19:12.482 --> 19:13.573
I'M GONNA HAVE SOMEONE PULL
THE SURVEILLANCE VIDEO

19:13.573 --> 19:15.154
FROM THE HOTEL THAT NIGHT.

19:15.154 --> 19:18.658
BUT, IN THE MEANTIME, I NEED
TO TALK TO THE PAVELS AGAIN.

19:18.658 --> 19:20.740
CAN I ASK --
WERE SILVIE AND ELENA

19:20.740 --> 19:23.493
HAVING ANY PROBLEMS
AT WORK?

19:23.493 --> 19:26.336
[ SIGHS ]

19:26.336 --> 19:29.589
S-SILVIE NEVER SHARED THAT SORT
OF THING WITH ME.

19:29.589 --> 19:31.251
I WISH I HAD THAT KIND
OF RELATIONSHIP WITH HER,

19:31.251 --> 19:34.674
BUT I WAS ALWAYS TOO BUSY
TRYING TO PUT FOOD ON THE TABLE.

19:34.674 --> 19:38.848
WHEN SHE HAD A PROBLEM,
SHE'D GO TO HER MOM.

19:38.848 --> 19:40.600
WHY ARE YOU ASKING
ABOUT PROBLEMS?

19:40.600 --> 19:42.602
WE'RE TRYING TO DETERMINE

19:42.602 --> 19:45.435
IF THERE WAS
A MOTIVE INVOLVED.

19:45.435 --> 19:47.517
YOU JUST SAID THAT THE WOMAN
WENT CRAZY.

19:47.517 --> 19:49.769
I THOUGHT WE WERE TALKING
AN INSANITY PLEA.

19:49.769 --> 19:51.941
WE'RE LOOKING INTO THE IDEA
THAT ELENA...

19:51.941 --> 19:55.615
MAY NOT HAVE BEEN ENTIRELY
TRUTHFUL ABOUT THAT.

19:55.615 --> 19:57.196
S-SO, Y-YOU THINK
SHE FAKED THIS ILLNESS?

19:57.196 --> 19:59.409
NO, NO,
SHE HAD A REAL CONDITION,

19:59.409 --> 20:03.202
BUT IT'S POSSIBLE SHE WAS SANE
WHEN SHE KILLED YOUR DAUGHTER.

20:03.202 --> 20:06.035
SHE MURDERED SILVIE
IN COLD BLOOD?

20:07.457 --> 20:09.879
YOU KNOW, WHEN SILVIE
GRADUATED FORM STANFORD,

20:09.879 --> 20:12.292
I-I WANTED HER TO WORK FOR ME
LIKE HER BROTHERS,

20:12.292 --> 20:16.926
BUT, UM...
SHE WANTED TO HELP PEOPLE.

20:16.926 --> 20:19.549
AND LOOK WHERE
IT GOT HER.

20:19.549 --> 20:24.474
PLEASE, YOU MAKE SURE YOU GET
JUSTICE FOR OUR LITTLE GIRL.

20:34.564 --> 20:35.855
Donnie: HEY.
HEY.

20:35.855 --> 20:37.737
WHAT'S UP?
I'M JUST TRYING TO ESTABLISH

20:37.737 --> 20:40.239
ELENA'S WHEREABOUTS
AT THE TIME OF THE MURDER.

20:40.239 --> 20:41.911
BUT I DID PICK UP
SOME HOP-LI

20:41.911 --> 20:44.324
AND THOSE LITTLE
CHOCOLATE THINGS

20:44.324 --> 20:46.416
THAT YOU LIKE FROM
LET THEM EAT CUPCAKES.

20:46.416 --> 20:48.328
YOU TRYING TO BRIBE ME?

20:48.328 --> 20:51.250
I AM TRYING TO BUY
YOUR FORGIVENESS.

20:51.250 --> 20:53.753
WHAT DID YOU DO?

20:56.336 --> 20:57.507
UM...

20:59.429 --> 21:04.013
THERE'S BEEN A LITTLE BIT
OF A HITCH WITH THE ANNULMENT.

21:04.013 --> 21:06.265
YEAH?
YEAH.

21:06.265 --> 21:08.267
I THOUGHT FATHER PAT SAID
EVERYTHING WAS COPACETIC.

21:08.267 --> 21:09.689
IT WAS. IT WAS.

21:09.689 --> 21:12.692
AND THEN I MADE IT
A LITTLE BIT...

21:12.692 --> 21:15.695
LESS COPACETIC
BY PISSING OFF THE MONSIGNOR.

21:15.695 --> 21:17.777
AND NOW IF I DON'T ADMIT
THAT I WAS WRONG,

21:17.777 --> 21:20.450
OUR WEDDING
ISN'T HAPPENING.

21:20.450 --> 21:23.112
AND YOU DON'T THINK
YOU WERE WRONG.

21:23.112 --> 21:24.664
I KNOW FOR A FACT
THAT I WAS NOT WRONG,

21:24.664 --> 21:27.537
SO HOW CAN I LOOK HIM
IN THE EYES AND SAY THAT I WAS?

21:27.537 --> 21:30.169
LOOK, DON,
YOU KNOW THAT I UNDERSTAND

21:30.169 --> 21:32.582
THAT A CHURCH WEDDING
IS IMPORTANT TO YOU.

21:32.582 --> 21:35.875
KATE. IT'S FINE.

21:35.875 --> 21:37.967
I WOULD NEVER ASK YOU TO
SACRIFICE YOUR PRINCIPLES.

21:37.967 --> 21:39.969
WE'LL BOOK
THE FOUR SEASONS.

21:39.969 --> 21:41.130
AND WE'RE GOOD?

21:41.130 --> 21:43.222
YES. WE'RE GOOD.

21:43.222 --> 21:46.556
I'LL GO SET THE TABLE.

21:48.558 --> 21:50.309
[ SIGHS ]

22:00.780 --> 22:03.783
YOU'VE GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

22:03.783 --> 22:06.536
THIS IS ELENA LEAVING JAKE'S
HOTEL ROOM CLEARLY A BIT DRUNK.

22:06.536 --> 22:12.452
SHE RIDES THE ELEVATOR DOWN,
GETS OFF AT 9:18.

22:12.452 --> 22:18.297
SHE GOES TO THE PARKING LOT,
GETS IN HER CAR, AND THEN...

22:18.297 --> 22:20.049
WHAT?
NOTHING'S HAPPENING.

22:20.049 --> 22:21.421
EXACTLY.

22:21.421 --> 22:22.762
THE CAR DOESN'T BUDGE
FOR THE NEXT SIX HOURS.

22:22.762 --> 22:25.845
SHE WAS SLEEPING IT OFF.

22:25.845 --> 22:27.517
OUT COLD AT THE TIME
OF THE MURDER,

22:27.517 --> 22:29.519
WHICH EXPLAINS WHY THE FORENSICS
CAME BACK CLEAN ON THE CAR.

22:29.519 --> 22:30.850
SHE COULDN'T HAVE
KILLED SILVIE.

22:30.850 --> 22:32.522
SO WHY CONFESS?

22:32.522 --> 22:35.605
SHE'S OBVIOUSLY LYING TO
COVER UP FOR THE REAL KILLER.

22:39.278 --> 22:42.111
LISTEN, ELENA,
YOU'RE A WOMAN OF FAITH.

22:42.111 --> 22:45.535
YOU KNOW THAT CONFESSION IS
ABOUT UNBURDENING YOUR SECRETS.

22:45.535 --> 22:48.287
IT'S ABOUT FINDING ABSOLUTION.
DON'T YOU WANT THAT?

22:48.287 --> 22:50.910
MY CLIENT HAS NOTHING
TO CONFESS.

22:50.910 --> 22:52.622
IN FACT,
SHE'S RELIEVED TO LEARN

22:52.622 --> 22:54.454
SHE DIDN'T DO
THIS TERRIBLE THING.

22:54.454 --> 22:56.085
AND SINCE YOU HAVE
EXCULPATORY EVIDENCE,

22:56.085 --> 22:59.128
DROP THE CHARGES
AND LET HER GO HOME RIGHT NOW.

22:59.128 --> 23:00.760
ACTUALLY,
I THINK WE'LL CHARGE YOU

23:00.760 --> 23:02.672
WITH LYING TO
A FEDERAL AGENT INSTEAD.

23:02.672 --> 23:04.464
THAT AND OBSTRUCTION.

23:04.464 --> 23:07.467
UNLESS, OF COURSE, SHE WANTS
TO START TELLING US THE TRUTH.

23:07.467 --> 23:10.640
SHE WASN'T LYING.
SHE WAS CONFUSED.

23:12.141 --> 23:14.974
YOU'LL NEVER MAKE
THOSE CHARGES STICK.

23:16.476 --> 23:18.397
VOSS IS RIGHT.

23:18.397 --> 23:20.019
IT'D BE TOUGH
TO PROSECUTE HER.

23:20.019 --> 23:22.822
SHE'S NOT GOING TO TELL US
WHO SHE'S COVERING FOR.

23:22.822 --> 23:24.193
IF RICHARD AND SILVIE
WERE HAVING AN AFFAIR

23:24.193 --> 23:26.195
AND SILVIE WAS
GONNA TELL ELENA ABOUT IT,

23:26.195 --> 23:28.027
RICHARD COULD HAVE KILLED HER
TO KEEP IT QUIET.

23:28.027 --> 23:29.869
AND ELENA WAS WILLING
TO TAKE THE FALL

23:29.869 --> 23:31.491
FOR A HUSBAND
WHO CHEATED ON HER?

23:31.491 --> 23:32.872
YOU'D BE SURPRISED
WHAT WIVES

23:32.872 --> 23:35.495
ARE WILLING TO FORGIVE
THEIR HUSBANDS FOR.

23:37.416 --> 23:40.039
YOU THINK I KILLED SILVIE?!
THIS IS INSANE!

23:40.039 --> 23:43.002
YOU DON'T HAVE A SHRED
OF EVIDENCE

23:43.002 --> 23:44.844
AGAINST ME OR MY WIFE.

23:44.844 --> 23:48.177
A-AND I SURE AS HELL WASN'T
HAVING AN AFFAIR WITH THAT GIRL.

23:48.177 --> 23:49.639
ELENA THOUGHT
THAT YOU WERE.

23:49.639 --> 23:51.260
SHE OVERHEARD YOU AND SILVIE
TAKING ABOUT A SECRET.

23:51.260 --> 23:52.682
WHAT WAS IT?

23:52.682 --> 23:54.353
ELENA WAS SICK.

23:55.264 --> 23:57.517
W-WHO KNOWS WHAT
SHE THOUGHT SHE HEARD.

23:57.517 --> 23:59.148
WE DON'T THINK SHE WAS SICK
AT ALL AT THAT POINT.

23:59.148 --> 24:00.820
WHEN I INTERVIEWED YOU
LAST MONTH,

24:00.820 --> 24:03.523
YOU SAID THAT YOU WERE ALONE
AT WORK WHEN SILVIE WAS KILLED.

24:03.523 --> 24:05.695
YOU DON'T HAVE AN ALIBI.

24:08.117 --> 24:10.119
THAT WAS A LIE.

24:11.450 --> 24:13.783
I WAS WITH SOMEONE.

24:13.783 --> 24:14.874
WHO?

24:17.036 --> 24:19.248
I REALLY CAN'T TELL YOU ANYTHING
ABOUT MY CLIENTS.

24:19.248 --> 24:21.961
DOMINATRIX/SERVANT
PRIVILEGE AND ALL.

24:23.713 --> 24:27.136
SO, I ASSUME THAT YOU NEVER HAVE
ANY SEXUAL CONTACT

24:27.136 --> 24:28.798
WITH ANY OF YOUR CLIENTS.

24:28.798 --> 24:30.139
OF COURSE NOT.

24:30.139 --> 24:32.221
SO, YOU WOULD HAVE
NO PROBLEM

24:32.221 --> 24:34.644
IF THE FBI WANTED TO START
MAKING REGULAR VISITS

24:34.644 --> 24:37.767
TO THE, UH,
SUBMISSION SANCTUARY,

24:37.767 --> 24:39.228
MAYBE LOOK THROUGH
YOUR BOOKS,

24:39.228 --> 24:40.399
DUG THROUGH
YOUR BACKGROUND?

24:40.399 --> 24:43.693
I CAN MAKE YOUR LIFE

24:43.693 --> 24:44.904
EXTREMELY UNPLEASANT.

24:44.904 --> 24:46.235
MM.

24:46.235 --> 24:47.947
BABE, YOU MAY HAVE MISSED
YOUR CALLING.

24:47.947 --> 24:49.278
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:49.278 --> 24:51.370
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO KNOW?

24:54.914 --> 24:57.076
OH, YEAH.
YEAH.

24:57.076 --> 24:58.417
HE'S ONE OF MY REGULARS.

24:58.417 --> 25:01.250
WAS HE THERE THE NIGHT
OF MAY 18th?

25:01.250 --> 25:02.582
UM...

25:02.582 --> 25:05.084
OH, LOOKS LIKE IT.
YOU WANT CONFIRMATION?

25:06.756 --> 25:07.887
HOW?

25:07.887 --> 25:09.338
I HAVE TIME-STAMPED VIDEOS

25:09.338 --> 25:10.590
OF ALL OF MY SESSIONS,

25:10.590 --> 25:12.301
YOU KNOW,
TO PROTECT MYSELF.

25:13.392 --> 25:14.594
YOU WANT TO SEE?

25:14.594 --> 25:16.305
I-I'M GOOD.
I'LL TAKE THE HIT.

25:20.600 --> 25:22.732
Richard: DELICIOUS.

25:22.732 --> 25:24.854
Satan: GOD, I LOVE THIS WOMAN!
[ WHIP CRACKING, GROANING ]

25:24.854 --> 25:26.606
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU'RE PATHETIC.
COUNT FOR ME.

25:26.606 --> 25:28.107
ONE OF MY MANY MINIONS.
ONE.

25:28.107 --> 25:29.318
ONE OF THE BEST.

25:29.318 --> 25:31.320
TWO.
WE'LL GO TO A HUNDRED.

25:31.320 --> 25:34.033
VERY IMAGINATIVE WHEN IT COMES
TO INFLICTING PAIN.
AAH!

25:34.033 --> 25:36.035
AAH!
KNEEL.

25:36.035 --> 25:38.287
[ LAUGHS ]
AAH!

25:38.287 --> 25:41.040
MASOCHISTS PAY HER THOUSANDS
OF DOLLARS TO TORTURE THEM.

25:41.040 --> 25:42.962
DID I TELL YOU TO STOP?
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:42.962 --> 25:44.503
[ GROANS ]

25:44.503 --> 25:46.545
WHAT, YOU STILL NEED
MORE PROOF I EXIST?

25:46.545 --> 25:49.969
THOUSANDS OF DOLLARS?
UH-HUH.

25:49.969 --> 25:52.261
WHEN YOU SAY THAT RICHARD
WAS A REGULAR CUSTOMER,

25:52.261 --> 25:54.223
WHAT DOES THAT MEAN IN DOLLARS
AND CENTS?

25:54.223 --> 25:56.135
WELL, HE SESSIONED
ABOUT TWICE A WEEK,

25:56.135 --> 25:58.517
USUALLY THE SWAT, SPANK,
AND WORSHIP PACKAGE.

25:58.517 --> 26:00.770
THAT'S ABOUT $1,500.

26:00.770 --> 26:02.441
A WEEK?
AN HOUR.

26:03.562 --> 26:06.025
MAYBE I DID
MISS MY CALLING.

26:06.025 --> 26:08.487
THAT IS ONE HELL OF A LOT MORE
THAN AN FBI PAYCHECK.

26:08.487 --> 26:10.239
IF RICHARD WENT THERE
TWICE A WEEK,

26:10.239 --> 26:11.781
THAT'S OVER 100 GRAND
A YEAR.

26:11.781 --> 26:13.322
THESE PEOPLE WORK
FOR A NONPROFIT.

26:13.322 --> 26:14.824
SO HOW WAS HE PAYING FOR IT?

26:14.824 --> 26:16.786
WELL, IF THE CHARITY'S RAKING IN
THAT MUCH CASH,

26:16.786 --> 26:18.157
MAYBE HE'S SKIMMING
OFF THE TOP.

26:18.157 --> 26:20.249
SO, THE CONVERSATION
THAT ELENA OVERHEARD

26:20.249 --> 26:22.201
COULD HAVE BEEN SILVIE
TELLING RICHARD

26:22.201 --> 26:24.413
THAT SHE WAS GONNA EXPOSE
HIS EMBEZZLEMENT,

26:24.413 --> 26:25.705
NOT ABOUT SOME AFFAIR.

26:25.705 --> 26:27.506
THAT WOULD GIVE HIM MOTIVE
FOR MURDER.

26:27.506 --> 26:30.259
ALTHOUGH, AS WE JUST
ESTABLISHED, HE HAS AN ALIBI.

26:30.259 --> 26:33.552
WE'VE ALSO ESTABLISHED THAT
HE CAN AFFORD TO HIRE A HITMAN.

26:33.552 --> 26:37.136
I'M GONNA ASK DONNIE FOR
A WARRANT FOR NRP's BOOKS.

26:40.680 --> 26:42.271
YOU STALKING ME,
FATHER PAT?

26:42.271 --> 26:44.183
I WAS JUST CATCHING UP
WITH DONNIE.

26:44.183 --> 26:46.525
HE SAYS YOU'RE GETTING HITCHED
AT THE FOUR SEASONS?
YEAH.

26:46.525 --> 26:48.397
TURNS OUT HE'S FINE WITH IT.

26:48.397 --> 26:50.109
COME ON.

26:50.109 --> 26:51.781
YOU AND I BOTH KNOW HE HAD
HIS HEART SET ON ST. MARY'S.

26:51.781 --> 26:54.533
KATE,
IT'S HIS WAY OF ATONING

26:54.533 --> 26:56.786
FOR THE MISTAKES HE MADE
IN YOUR FIRST MARRIAGE.

26:56.786 --> 26:58.788
YOU GOT TO LET
THE MAN ATONE.

26:58.788 --> 27:02.241
LISTEN, EVEN IF I WANTED TO,
HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO DO THAT?

27:02.241 --> 27:04.293
I APOLOGIZED
TO THE MONSIGNOR.

27:04.293 --> 27:05.624
HE DIDN'T ACCEPT IT.

27:05.624 --> 27:07.246
COME ON, KATIE.
THIS IS CHICAGO.

27:07.246 --> 27:08.838
THE MONSIGNOR'S OLD-SCHOOL.
YOU KNOW HOW IT WORKS.

27:08.838 --> 27:10.339
YOU DO SOMETHING NICE
FOR THE CHURCH,

27:10.339 --> 27:11.630
HE DOES SOMETHING NICE
FOR YOU.

27:11.630 --> 27:12.882
WHAT IS THIS,
A SHAKEDOWN NOW?

27:12.882 --> 27:14.303
FEELS LIKE A SHAKEDOWN.

27:14.303 --> 27:16.806
CALL IT AN ACT OF CONTRITION,
ALL RIGHT?

27:16.806 --> 27:18.718
THE MONSIGNOR CARES
ABOUT THE CHURCH, OKAY?

27:18.718 --> 27:20.890
THE COLLECTION PLATE'S BEEN
A LITTLE LIGHT LATELY.

27:20.890 --> 27:22.641
WE'RE HOLDING AN AUCTION
FRIDAY NIGHT.

27:22.641 --> 27:25.104
SHOW UP AND BUY
SOMETHING EXPENSIVE.

27:25.104 --> 27:28.027
I DON'T KNOW.
THIS FEELS WRONG.

27:28.027 --> 27:29.568
YOU KNOW WHAT I THINK?
HMM?

27:29.568 --> 27:31.400
THIS ISN'T ABOUT NORRIS
OR YOUR PRINCIPLES.

27:31.400 --> 27:32.692
THIS IS ABOUT THE TOMBOY

27:32.692 --> 27:34.193
THAT I KNEW BACK
ON THE PLAYGROUND

27:34.193 --> 27:35.614
WHO HATES THE IDEA

27:35.614 --> 27:36.946
OF STANDING IN FRONT
OF THE ALTAR

27:36.946 --> 27:38.828
AT ST. MARY'S
IN A BIG, POUFY DRESS.

27:38.828 --> 27:41.741
Okay, so what if I do?

27:41.741 --> 27:43.743
WELL, THEN, DONNIE
HAS GOT TO SACRIFICE

27:43.743 --> 27:46.495
WHAT'S IMPORTANT TO HIM
BECAUSE YOU'RE JUST NOT WILLING

27:46.495 --> 27:48.417
TO SACRIFICE
WHAT'S IMPORTANT TO YOU.

27:50.629 --> 27:52.671
[ SIGHS ]

27:52.671 --> 27:55.464
OH, YEAH.
I GOT YOU NOW, DOC.

27:55.464 --> 27:57.927
ROOK TO A3.
I TAKE YOUR BISHOP.

27:59.678 --> 28:00.639
[ SIGHS ]

28:00.639 --> 28:03.262
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

28:03.262 --> 28:04.393
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]

28:04.393 --> 28:06.645
DR. PIERCE'S RESIDENCE.

28:06.645 --> 28:10.359
DOC, IT'S KATE.
IT SOUNDS IMPORTANT.

28:10.359 --> 28:13.232
Kate: CHECK THIS OUT.
WE WENT THROUGH NRP's BOOKS.

28:13.232 --> 28:14.483
WAS RICHARD EMBEZZLING?

28:14.483 --> 28:16.235
WE FOUND SOMETHING
EVEN BETTER.

28:16.235 --> 28:20.820
THE CHARITY TAKES IN
ABOUT $600,000 A YEAR.

28:20.820 --> 28:23.082
$300,000 OF THAT COMES
FROM CORPORATE DONATIONS.

28:23.082 --> 28:25.534
THE REST IS FROM INDIVIDUALS
WHO GIVE THROUGH PayPal,

28:25.534 --> 28:28.207
CHECK, OR GOOD
OLD-FASHIONED CASH,

28:28.207 --> 28:29.789
WHICH ACCOUNTS FOR...

28:29.789 --> 28:31.710
$10,000 A MONTH,

28:31.710 --> 28:34.003
UNTIL LAST FEBRUARY,

28:34.003 --> 28:37.797
WHEN CASH DONATIONS SPIKED
TO $300,000.

28:37.797 --> 28:42.301
CORPORATE GIVING STAYS THE SAME,
AND CASH GOES UP 3,000%?

28:42.301 --> 28:43.893
MM-HMM.

28:43.893 --> 28:46.345
AND THEN, ALL OF THAT NEW MONEY
IS CYCLED RIGHT BACK OUT

28:46.345 --> 28:48.227
TO HUNDREDS
OF NEW MICROLOAN RECIPIENTS.

28:48.227 --> 28:49.849
I'M BETTING
THEY DON'T EVEN EXIST.

28:49.849 --> 28:51.350
THIS CHARITY'S A FRONT

28:51.350 --> 28:54.113
FOR A MASSIVE
MONEY-LAUNDERING OPERATION.

28:54.113 --> 28:57.566
DON'T YOU JUST LOVE
THE HYPOCRISY?

29:03.913 --> 29:07.366
THE DOUGLAS FAMILY SURE PROVIDES
YOU WITH A LOT OF BUSINESS.

29:07.366 --> 29:09.668
YOU NEED TO STOP BRINGING
SPURIOUS CHARGES

29:09.668 --> 29:10.830
AGAINST MY CLIENTS.

29:10.830 --> 29:11.961
Kate:
WE HAVE HARD EVIDENCE

29:11.961 --> 29:13.502
THAT AT LEAST A QUARTER

29:13.502 --> 29:15.214
OF THE CHARITY'S MICROLOAN
RECIPIENTS ARE FAKE.

29:15.214 --> 29:17.296
WHO ARE YOU
LAUNDERING MONEY FOR?

29:17.296 --> 29:20.259
ONCE AGAIN, MY CLIENT
HAS NOTHING TO SAY.

29:20.259 --> 29:22.051
THAT'S FINE.
I'LL DO THE TALKING.

29:22.051 --> 29:24.143
SILVIE FOUND OUT ABOUT THE MONEY
LAUNDERING AND CONFRONTED YOU.

29:24.143 --> 29:26.345
SHE THREATENED TO EXPOSE
YOUR OPERATION,

29:26.345 --> 29:28.057
SO YOU HAD HER KILLED
TO KEEP HER QUIET.

29:28.057 --> 29:30.269
THAT'S A FAIRY TALE.

29:30.269 --> 29:32.771
YOU HAVE NO EVIDENCE
OF ANY MURDER.

29:32.771 --> 29:34.443
AND IF YOU'RE LOOKING
FOR FRAUD,

29:34.443 --> 29:36.235
FIND THE SWINDLERS WHO CREATED
FALSE IDENTITIES

29:36.235 --> 29:37.987
TO GET LOANS FROM MY CLIENTS.

29:37.987 --> 29:40.109
WE'RE DONE HERE.

29:42.401 --> 29:45.284
THE BIGGEST PROBLEM
IN ALBANY PARK IS DRUGS.

29:45.284 --> 29:46.996
MAYBE RICHARD'S LAUNDERING MONEY
FOR ONE OF THE DEALERS.

29:46.996 --> 29:48.457
THE -- THE -- THE --
THE GUY WE TALKED TO

29:48.457 --> 29:50.579
THAT GOT A ROOM WITH ELENA,
HE WAS AN EX-CON.

29:50.579 --> 29:52.581
WHAT WAS HE IN FOR?

29:52.581 --> 29:55.174
HELL, EVEN WHEN I WAS DEALING,
I NEVER MOVED THAT MUCH MONEY.

29:55.174 --> 29:56.465
I WOULDN'T EVEN BEGIN TO KNOW

29:56.465 --> 29:58.047
HOW TO RUN AN OPERATION
THAT SIZE.

29:58.047 --> 29:59.718
BUT YOU DON'T SEEM
TOO SURPRISED

29:59.718 --> 30:02.381
THAT NRP WAS A LAUNDROMAT
FOR DIRTY CASH.

30:04.723 --> 30:05.925
COME ON, JAKE.
TELL US WHAT YOU KNOW.

30:05.925 --> 30:07.386
I DON'T RAT PEOPLE OUT.

30:07.386 --> 30:09.348
THAT'S A CODE I'VE LIVED BY
MY WHOLE LIFE.

30:09.348 --> 30:11.480
SEE, YOU DON'T GET TO HAVE IT
BOTH WAYS.

30:11.480 --> 30:13.102
YOU'RE EITHER
TRULY REFORMED,

30:13.102 --> 30:15.024
OR YOU'RE CLEANING DRUG MONEY
FOR SOME SCUMBAG.

30:15.024 --> 30:17.316
NOW, YOU GOT TO CHOOSE
BETWEEN GOOD AND EVIL.

30:17.316 --> 30:18.697
DON'T TALK TO ME
ABOUT GOOD AND EVIL.

30:18.697 --> 30:20.279
THERE'S NO SUCH THING.

30:20.279 --> 30:22.441
WHAT ABOUT SILVIE?
YOU DON'T THINK SHE WAS GOOD?

30:22.441 --> 30:23.863
YOU THINK
SHE DESERVED WHAT SHE GOT?

30:23.863 --> 30:25.865
[ SIGHS ]

30:28.537 --> 30:31.830
LOOK...

30:31.830 --> 30:36.665
YOU PUT ME ON THE STAND,
AND I'LL DENY ALL OF THIS.

30:36.665 --> 30:40.089
BUT, YEAH,
SILVIE CAME TO ME.

30:40.089 --> 30:43.963
SHE WAS...SMART.

30:43.963 --> 30:46.966
SHE'D FOUND THE DISCREPANCY
IN THE BOOKS.

30:46.966 --> 30:49.308
THE CHARITY'S A FRAUD,
AND RICHARD, TOO.

30:49.308 --> 30:51.600
HE BEGGED ME
NOT TO TELL ELENA.

30:51.600 --> 30:53.182
WE DO A LOT
OF GOOD WORK HERE, SILVIE.

30:53.182 --> 30:54.683
WHO CARES IF PEOPLE
TAKE THEIR CUT?

30:54.683 --> 30:55.814
THAT'S THE WAY
THE WORLD WORKS.

30:55.814 --> 30:57.316
I CAN'T LIVE WITH THAT.

30:57.316 --> 30:58.817
SILVIE, WAIT!

31:00.689 --> 31:03.402
I TOLD HER TO CHILL,

31:03.402 --> 31:06.075
BUT SHE WAS SO NAIVE.

31:06.075 --> 31:09.158
SHE SAID HER FATHER HAD DONATED
THOUSANDS OF DOLLARS.

31:09.158 --> 31:11.951
SHE HAD TO TELL HER FAMILY
THE TRUTH ABOUT NRP.

31:11.951 --> 31:15.124
[ SCOFFS ] AND I TOLD HER MAYBE
THAT WASN'T SUCH A GOOD IDEA.

31:15.124 --> 31:16.875
WHY NOT?

31:16.875 --> 31:21.130
BECAUSE SHE'D FIND OUT SOMETHING
SHE DIDN'T WANT TO KNOW.

31:23.002 --> 31:24.593
LOOK, EVERY COUPLE WEEKS,

31:24.593 --> 31:27.216
I'D SEE RICHARD GET
A LATE-NIGHT CASH DELIVERY.

31:27.216 --> 31:29.468
AND THE GUYS DROPPING OFF
THE MONEY...

31:31.140 --> 31:33.062
...THEY WERE PAVEL'S SONS.

31:37.566 --> 31:39.568
John:
YOU'VE GOT NOTHING ON US.

31:39.568 --> 31:42.861
WE'VE GOT DEPOSIT SLIPS,
WIRELESS TRANSFER RECEIPTS,

31:42.861 --> 31:44.823
AND REAMS OF ACCOUNT DATA,

31:44.823 --> 31:46.695
ALL PROVING
THAT YOUR DIRTY MONEY

31:46.695 --> 31:48.407
WAS WASHED
THROUGH THE CHARITY

31:48.407 --> 31:50.829
AND THEN DEPOSITED IN A SECRET
ACCOUNT IN THE CAYMANS.

31:50.829 --> 31:53.993
NOW, I'M GUESSING THAT YOU
DIDN'T MAKE ALL THAT CASH

31:53.993 --> 31:55.704
INSTALLING LAMINATE FLOORING,

31:55.704 --> 31:58.797
SO, WHAT WAS IT -- DRUGS,
PROSTITUTION?

31:58.797 --> 31:59.999
HOW DARE YOU SPEAK TO MY HUSBAND
LIKE THAT!

31:59.999 --> 32:01.250
THAT'S ALL RIGHT,
SWEETHEART.

32:01.250 --> 32:02.301
THESE ALLEGATIONS
ARE LUDICROUS.

32:02.301 --> 32:03.632
SILVIE DIDN'T THINK SO.

32:03.632 --> 32:04.633
SHE TOLD YOU SHE WAS GOING

32:04.633 --> 32:05.965
TO THE AUTHORITIES.

32:05.965 --> 32:08.507
SHE WOULD HAVE RUINED
YOUR FAMILY,

32:08.507 --> 32:10.219
SO YOU HAD HER KILLED.
MY OWN DAUGHTER?

32:10.219 --> 32:11.720
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU'RE CRAZY!

32:11.720 --> 32:13.432
I LOVED SILVIE!
I WOULDN'T HURT MY OWN DAUGHTER!

32:13.432 --> 32:14.683
YOU KNOW,
I'M NOT SAYING ANOTHER WORD.

32:14.683 --> 32:16.605
I WANT MY LAWYER.
OH, THAT'S RIGHT.

32:16.605 --> 32:18.357
YOU'RE REPRESENTED
BY THE SAME FIRM

32:18.357 --> 32:19.858
THAT EMPLOYS BRENDAN VOSS,

32:19.858 --> 32:22.861
THE LAWYER WHO ENTERED
ELENA'S INSANITY PLEA,

32:22.861 --> 32:25.824
ONLY HE WASN'T LOOKING OUT
FOR HER INTERESTS.

32:25.824 --> 32:27.446
HE WAS PROTECTING YOURS.

32:27.446 --> 32:29.738
SO, HOW'D YOU GET HER
TO CONFESS?

32:29.738 --> 32:31.200
DID YOU THREATEN
TO KILL HER, TOO?

32:33.452 --> 32:34.783
Kate: COME ON.
LET'S GO.

32:34.783 --> 32:36.495
IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT,
HONEY.

32:36.495 --> 32:38.207
IT'S GONNA BE OKAY.
DON'T WORRY.

32:41.670 --> 32:44.583
I THOUGHT MAX WAS GONNA BE
EASY PICKINGS.

32:44.583 --> 32:47.296
IT'S NOT THE GAME
THAT'S BOTHERING ME.

32:47.296 --> 32:48.717
THEN WHAT?

32:48.717 --> 32:52.051
Satan:
WE MADE A DEAL, DANNY.

32:52.051 --> 32:54.303
BUT YOU HAVEN'T SIGNED
THE CONTRACT.

32:54.303 --> 32:56.555
I JUST NEED YOUR JOHN HANCOCK
RIGHT HERE,

32:56.555 --> 32:59.148
AND THEN I'LL LET YOU IN
ON WHAT'S TROUBLING YOU.

33:00.269 --> 33:02.561
DANIEL.

33:02.561 --> 33:04.483
[ SIGHS ] OHH.

33:04.483 --> 33:07.316
HE'S NOT REAL,
AND NEITHER IS HELL,

33:07.316 --> 33:09.238
SO, WHY THE HELL NOT?

33:09.238 --> 33:11.740
[ CHUCKLES ]
THANKS.

33:11.740 --> 33:15.244
YOU KNOW, I'M REALLY GONNA ENJOY
SPENDING ETERNITY WITH YOU.

33:15.244 --> 33:17.416
OKAY, HERE'S YOUR PROBLEM.

33:17.416 --> 33:20.959
IN FOUR MOVES,
LEWICKI'S GONNA CHECKMATE YOU.

33:22.581 --> 33:24.173
SON OF A BITCH.

33:24.173 --> 33:26.004
YOU'RE NOT GONNA LET HIM GET
AWAY WITH THAT, ARE YOU?

33:26.004 --> 33:28.467
GET AWAY WITH WHAT?
MAX PLAYED WELL.

33:28.467 --> 33:29.508
NO, HE DIDN'T.
HE CHEATED.

33:29.508 --> 33:30.549
HE MOVED HIS QUEEN

33:30.549 --> 33:32.301
WHEN YOU WEREN'T LOOKING.

33:32.301 --> 33:35.013
IT'S THE ONLY WAY HE COULD HAVE
PULLED OFF THIS GAMBIT.

33:35.013 --> 33:37.096
HE'S RIGHT.

33:37.096 --> 33:38.517
DANIEL,
DON'T BE PARANOID.

33:38.517 --> 33:39.598
MAX WOULD NEVER CHEAT.

33:39.598 --> 33:41.350
OF COURSE HE WOULD.

33:41.350 --> 33:42.771
EVERYBODY CHEATS.

33:42.771 --> 33:44.523
IT'S ONE OF MY GREATEST
ACCOMPLISHMENTS.

33:45.694 --> 33:47.606
MOVE IT BACK.
DON'T!

33:49.778 --> 33:53.452
UH, DOC,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

33:55.074 --> 33:56.785
ARE YOU CHEATING?

33:56.785 --> 33:58.367
NO. YOU WERE!

33:58.367 --> 34:00.619
YOU CLEARLY MOVED MY QUEEN
WHEN I WASN'T LOOKING.

34:00.619 --> 34:02.211
IF THAT'S THE WAY
YOU WANT TO --

34:04.583 --> 34:06.255
GOTCHA.

34:09.428 --> 34:13.432
I'M SORRY.
I JUST GOT A LITTLE CONFUSED.

34:13.432 --> 34:14.763
ARE YOU OKAY?

34:14.763 --> 34:16.885
YES, I'M FINE.

34:16.885 --> 34:18.177
THEN PUT MY QUEEN BACK
SO I CAN TAKE YOUR KNIGHT.

34:18.177 --> 34:20.389
Satan: YES, THE QUEEN.

34:20.389 --> 34:23.061
SHE CAN TAKE OUT ANY PIECE
ON THE BOARD.

34:25.734 --> 34:27.446
I --

34:27.446 --> 34:28.817
I GOT TO CALL KATE.

34:28.817 --> 34:31.110
WHY? WHAT'S WRONG?
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]

34:31.110 --> 34:32.991
WE WERE WRONG.
[ TELEPHONE SPEED DIALING ]

34:32.991 --> 34:35.194
JOHN PAVEL
DIDN'T KILL HIS DAUGHTER.
[ Telephone rings ]

34:41.540 --> 34:44.793
UNLESS YOU'VE GOT
ANOTHER WARRANT,

34:44.793 --> 34:47.466
YOU CAN JUST GET THE HELL
OFF MY PROPERTY.

34:47.466 --> 34:49.338
YOU'RE VERY PROTECTIVE
OF YOUR FAMILY,

34:49.338 --> 34:50.839
AREN'T YOU, MRS. PAVEL?

34:50.839 --> 34:52.711
IRONICALLY, THAT'S WHY
YOU KILLED YOUR DAUGHTER.

34:52.711 --> 34:54.633
THAT'S PREPOSTEROUS.

34:54.633 --> 34:56.215
THE LAST TIME I WAS HERE,

34:56.215 --> 34:58.016
YOUR HUSBAND WAS PRETTY
BROKEN UP ABOUT SILVIE,

34:58.016 --> 34:59.308
BUT YOU WERE CALM.

34:59.308 --> 35:00.809
HE WAS PARTICULARLY
GRIEF-STRICKEN

35:00.809 --> 35:02.601
THAT HE HADN'T BEEN CLOSER
WITH HER.

35:02.601 --> 35:05.314
YOU'RE THE ONE SHE ALWAYS TALKED
TO WHEN SHE HAD A PROBLEM.

35:05.314 --> 35:08.066
THAT'S WHY, WHEN SHE HEARD
ABOUT THE MONEY LAUNDERING,

35:08.066 --> 35:10.319
IT WASN'T HIM SHE WENT TO.
SHE CAME TO YOU.

35:10.319 --> 35:12.361
AND WHEN SHE TOLD YOU SHE WAS
GONNA GO TO THE AUTHORITIES,

35:12.361 --> 35:15.234
YOU SACRIFICED HER,

35:15.234 --> 35:17.656
YOUR ONLY DAUGHTER,
TO SAVE THE REST OF THEM.

35:17.656 --> 35:18.787
THAT'S A LIE.

35:18.787 --> 35:20.239
MRS. PAVEL...

35:20.239 --> 35:22.241
WE'RE IMPOUNDING
YOUR CAR.

35:22.241 --> 35:23.662
WE'RE ALSO PULLING
REPAIR RECORDS

35:23.662 --> 35:24.953
FROM EVERY SHOP
IN THE STATE.

35:24.953 --> 35:26.375
WE'RE GONNA PROVE
THAT IT WAS YOU.

35:26.375 --> 35:27.956
SO TELL US WHAT HAPPENED,

35:27.956 --> 35:31.049
AND MAYBE I CAN TALK TO
THE U.S. ATTORNEY ABOUT A DEAL.

35:31.049 --> 35:33.882
YOU AND YOUR HUSBAND
WOULD GO TO JAIL,

35:33.882 --> 35:35.924
BUT YOUR SONS
COULD GET PROBATION.

35:35.924 --> 35:38.347
THEY COULD STILL
HAVE A LIFE.

35:38.347 --> 35:41.930
OR I COULD MAKE IT
MY MISSION

35:41.930 --> 35:44.683
TO ENSURE THAT THEY SPEND AS
MUCH TIME IN PRISON AS POSSIBLE,

35:44.683 --> 35:47.396
THE FAMILY THAT YOU KILLED
YOUR DAUGHTER TO PROTECT

35:47.396 --> 35:48.477
WOULD BE RUINED.

35:48.477 --> 35:50.649
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

35:55.444 --> 35:58.577
SILVIE CALLED ME.
[ SNIFFLES ]

35:58.577 --> 36:01.240
SHE WAS RANTING ABOUT
THE CHARITY BEING A FRAUD

36:01.240 --> 36:03.872
AND TALKING ABOUT
GOING TO THE POLICE.

36:03.872 --> 36:07.045
Silvie: NRP IS JUST A GIANT
FRONT FOR MONEY LAUNDERING.

36:07.045 --> 36:10.048
I HAVE TO TELL THE POLICE.

36:10.048 --> 36:11.920
DON'T GET INVOLVED, SILVIE.

36:11.920 --> 36:14.673
WHAT? NO.

36:14.673 --> 36:17.636
I...I CAN'T JUST SIT BY
AND DO NOTHING.

36:17.636 --> 36:19.798
WELL, YOU HAVE TO.

36:19.798 --> 36:21.560
WHY?

36:23.562 --> 36:27.726
MOM?

36:27.726 --> 36:30.729
BECAUSE --

36:30.729 --> 36:33.732
BECAUSE IT'S OUR FAMILY'S MONEY
THAT'S BEING LAUNDERED.

36:37.316 --> 36:38.657
THAT'S NOT TRUE.

36:38.657 --> 36:40.279
DID YOU REALLY THINK

36:40.279 --> 36:41.320
THAT A FLOORING BUSINESS
SUPPORTED OUR LIFESTYLE...

36:41.320 --> 36:43.081
YOUR EDUCATION?

36:43.081 --> 36:45.163
GROW UP, SILVIE!

36:45.163 --> 36:47.746
WHERE DOES THE MONEY
COME FROM, THEN?

36:47.746 --> 36:51.250
DRUGS, EXTORTION, WORSE?!

36:51.250 --> 36:52.961
LOOK, IT'S YOUR FATHER'S
BUSINESS.

36:52.961 --> 36:54.423
HE AND THE BOYS PROVIDE,

36:54.423 --> 36:56.094
AND IT IS NOT OUR PLACE
TO ASK QUESTIONS!

36:56.094 --> 36:57.836
WHY?!
BECAUSE WE'RE WOMEN?

36:57.836 --> 36:59.838
BECAUSE I DON'T MATTER
TO YOU

36:59.838 --> 37:02.100
AS MUCH AS
YOUR PRECIOUS SONS?!

37:02.100 --> 37:04.603
YOU DISGUST ME!

37:06.435 --> 37:08.397
MY ENTIRE LIFE WAS A LIE,

37:08.397 --> 37:11.189
AND YOU NEVER SAID
ONE SINGLE WORD.

37:12.441 --> 37:15.694
I DON'T CARE
WHAT HAPPENS, MOM!

37:15.694 --> 37:16.855
I'M GOING TO THE POLICE.

37:16.855 --> 37:18.026
NO! YOU CAN'T!

37:18.026 --> 37:21.280
SILVIE, YOU CAN'T!
AAH!

37:21.280 --> 37:22.491
GO TO HELL!

37:22.491 --> 37:24.122
DON'T YOU
GET OUT OF THIS CAR!

37:24.122 --> 37:25.624
DON'T! SILVIE!

37:33.462 --> 37:34.963
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER,
TIRES SCREECH ]

37:34.963 --> 37:38.877
[ Crying ]
I HAD TO PROTECT MY FAMILY.

37:38.877 --> 37:42.381
I HAD TO SACRIFICE ONE
TO SAVE THE REST.

37:42.381 --> 37:44.222
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

37:47.386 --> 37:49.057
[ THUD ]

37:51.480 --> 37:53.312
[ BRAKES SQUEAL ]

37:57.776 --> 37:59.237
SO, WHEN YOU SAW THAT VIDEO,

37:59.237 --> 38:01.490
YOU KNEW THAT
IT WAS ONLY A MATTER OF TIME

38:01.490 --> 38:03.992
BEFORE THE FBI WOULD COME AROUND
ASKING ABOUT THE CHARITY.

38:03.992 --> 38:05.243
YOU PANICKED.

38:05.243 --> 38:07.075
YEAH, I CALLED VOSS.

38:07.075 --> 38:09.077
HE SAID HE HAD A PLAN.

38:09.077 --> 38:10.909
HE SAID DON'T WORRY.

38:10.909 --> 38:13.291
A FALSE CONFESSION.

38:13.291 --> 38:15.043
ELENA REALIZED
IT WAS THE ONLY WAY

38:15.043 --> 38:16.755
TO PROTECT HER HUSBAND
AND THE CHARITY,

38:16.755 --> 38:18.256
SO SHE WENT ALONG WITH IT.

38:18.256 --> 38:21.009
I THOUGHT MY FAMILY
WOULD BE SAVED.

38:21.009 --> 38:22.300
YOUR FAMILY WAS DESTROYED

38:22.300 --> 38:24.182
THE SECOND YOU KILLED
YOUR DAUGHTER.

38:24.182 --> 38:27.926
VICTORIA PAVEL,
YOU'RE UNDER ARREST FOR MURDER.

38:27.926 --> 38:29.688
[ HANDCUFFS CLICK ]

38:33.522 --> 38:38.397
MONSIGNOR, YOU ACCUSED ME
OF FALSE REPENTANCE BEFORE,

38:38.397 --> 38:41.440
AND, WELL,
YOU WERE RIGHT.

38:41.440 --> 38:43.111
TO MAKE UP FOR IT,

38:43.111 --> 38:46.114
I WOULD LIKE TO DO SOMETHING
FOR THE CHURCH.

38:49.448 --> 38:52.040
BLACKHAWKS
PLAYOFF TICKETS?
MM-HMM.

38:52.040 --> 38:53.912
YOU SHOULD BE ABLE TO GET
A FORTUNE FOR THEM

38:53.912 --> 38:55.544
TOMORROW
AT THE CHURCH RAFFLE.

38:55.544 --> 38:57.045
BLESS YOU, AGENT MORETTI.

39:01.550 --> 39:05.303
AND NOW I HAVE TO MAKE AMENDS
TO THE OTHER FATHER.

39:05.303 --> 39:07.135
[ DIALING ]

39:08.557 --> 39:11.059
HEY, DAD.

39:11.059 --> 39:12.891
UM...

39:12.891 --> 39:14.473
ABOUT THE GAME...

39:19.317 --> 39:21.319
THAT...

39:21.319 --> 39:23.572
WOULD BE CHECKMATE!

39:23.572 --> 39:24.693
YOU GOT TO BE KIDDING ME.

39:24.693 --> 39:27.075
[ CHUCKLES ]
GOTCHA!

39:27.075 --> 39:28.747
WHOO!

39:28.747 --> 39:30.579
[ HUMMING ] AH!

39:32.991 --> 39:36.585
WHO SAYS HELL ISN'T REAL?

39:40.088 --> 39:42.000
[ HUMMING CONTINUES ]

39:45.504 --> 39:47.466
[ SIGHS ]

39:47.466 --> 39:48.847
[ KEY CLINKS ]

39:50.429 --> 39:53.271
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT PAT DID...

39:53.271 --> 39:56.014
BUT THE WEDDING'S BACK ON
AT ST. MARY'S.

39:56.014 --> 39:57.355
REALLY?

39:57.355 --> 39:59.277
YEAH.
AW.

39:59.277 --> 40:00.859
GUESS THE MONSIGNOR
HAD A CHANGE OF HEART.

40:00.859 --> 40:03.111
MM-HMM.
MM-HMM.

40:03.111 --> 40:04.613
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:04.613 --> 40:07.285
STILL UP FOR MOVIE NIGHT
ON SATURDAY?

40:07.285 --> 40:09.287
WHAT ABOUT
THE BLACKHAWKS GAME?

40:09.287 --> 40:11.199
OH, COME ON, WHY WOULD I WANT
TO SPEND MY NIGHT

40:11.199 --> 40:13.662
WITH A BUNCH OF DRUNK,
OBNOXIOUS, SCREAMING FANS

40:13.662 --> 40:16.535
WHEN I COULD BE CURLED UP
ON THE COUCH...

40:16.535 --> 40:18.376
WITH THE MAN I LOVE?

40:21.880 --> 40:25.213
IF YOU BELIEVE IN THE GUY WITH
THE RED CAPE AND THE PITCHFORK,

40:25.213 --> 40:27.546
THEN THE WORLD IS DIVIDED UP
INTO GOOD AND EVIL.

40:27.546 --> 40:30.889
OF COURSE,
EVOLVED THINKERS LIKE US

40:30.889 --> 40:33.812
KNOW THAT LIFE'S
NOT QUITE SO ABSOLUTE.

40:33.812 --> 40:35.604
OR IS IT?

40:35.604 --> 40:38.767
fMRI SCANS OF PSYCHOPATHS

40:38.767 --> 40:41.229
REVEAL THAT THEIR BRAINS
HAVE SUBTLE DIFFERENCES.

40:41.229 --> 40:44.903
THERE'S LESS ACTIVITY
IN THEIR PREFRONTAL CORTICES

40:44.903 --> 40:46.565
AND DECREASED
REGIONAL GRAY MATTER

40:46.565 --> 40:48.617
IN THEIR PARALIMBIC SYSTEMS.

40:48.617 --> 40:54.162
IN OTHER WORDS,
THEY MAY BE WIRED TO DO EVIL.

40:54.162 --> 40:56.665
IT'S A SCARY THOUGHT.

40:56.665 --> 41:01.459
BUT EQUALLY AMAZING
IS OUR CAPACITY TO DO GOOD,

41:01.459 --> 41:05.383
THE BRAIN'S ABILITY
TO CREATE EMPATHY,

41:05.383 --> 41:10.799
COMPASSION, AND CONNECTION --

41:10.799 --> 41:13.972
THESE THINGS CAN GIVE SOMEONE
THE DRIVE

41:13.972 --> 41:16.144
TO LIVE A LIFE OF SACRIFICE...

41:18.767 --> 41:21.019
...OR TO COMMIT
TO SOMEONE THEY LOVE...

41:26.695 --> 41:29.698
...OR JUST TO CONNECT
WITH A FRIEND.
